{"tid":1532891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【切勿炒車，繼續罷買】大班即時喺微博出咗道歉聲明！","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:05:47.000Z","uid":75759,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07e27247b95bc5c67d1741feedfc8c09417bf276","tid":1532891,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"事緣大班太子爺fb笑鳩藍絲同share香港之路俾支那玻璃心聲言罷買，好多人就話要買大班支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYZT5W1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYZT5W1.jpg&h=d261ac9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係呢，電光火石之間大班就已經跪咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhcOapK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhcOapK.jpg&h=281ea8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為咗人民幣，大班麵包西餅 Taipan Bread &amp; Cakes已經同太子爺劃清界線。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話，佢都係被迫跪低姐，不分化不割席呀<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">當Chinaman代言間極深藍美心都唔落TVB嘅同時，大班喺反修例風波期間，於CCTVB落大量廣告(每晚黃金時段必定有)、贊助多個TVB節目，間接供養無綫新聞</span>：<br />\n1. 包青天<br />\n2. 吃貨48小時<br />\n3. 背包旅行之加勒比海<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位香港人繼續杯葛大班，直至大班承諾不再落TVB廣告！<br />\n如果承諾，中秋後我哋即刻復買大班！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每日洗版任務你今日做咗未？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾嬲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷買<br />\n每日任務(3/3)<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日洗版精選<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大班</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/snowymooncake/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsnowymooncake%2F&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=65548dd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/snowymooncake/</a><br />\n罪狀上面講咗<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幸福醫藥</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal%2F&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=f464d2ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/</a><br />\n罪狀：根據可靠資料顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">單單係八月份</span>，之前仲埋廣告打本土牌嘅&rdquo;幸福&rdquo;已經俾左約<span style=\"color: red;\">一千萬廣告費比CCTVB</span>。仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">大量市民早已經喺兩個月前要求撤回廣告，但&rdquo;幸福&rdquo;仍然無動於衷</span>。藥就賣到貴一貴，原來啲藥錢大部份俾CCTVB食咗，香港人真係好&ldquo;幸福&ldquo;啊...🙄<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舒適達</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SensodyneHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSensodyneHK%2F&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=588901e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SensodyneHK/</a><br />\n罪狀：接連幾日係TVB黃金時段<span style=\"color: red;\">頻繁出現</span>，登上樓豬嘅恥與為伍排行榜，且根據廣告界手足資料顯示，舒適達公司貢獻<span style=\"color: red;\">俾TVB嘅廣告費絕對可以登上頭十</span>，供養假新聞機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言Template，歡迎創意留言<br />\n1️⃣ <br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣ <br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍屍專用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看到贵公司在黄丝传媒CCTVB打广告，本人以及亲友们决定不会再支持贵公司"},{"pid":"44c27c8486c55513c1272bcc994a6a5d0da4e960","tid":1532891,"uid":75759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"抵制TVB好Easy，請到以下FB 追蹤TVB廣告，每日更新，恥與為伍！<br />\nLIKE數就是力量，嚇怕廣告客戶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2